Both  PubSub and PubSub Lite can be called using the Java Client library with few changes in dependencies. PubSub has a broader range of features then PubSub Lite but both are scalable and managed messaging services.
The difference while using PubSub and PubSub Lite is that while using PubSub Lite you need to add both PubSub and PubSub Lite artifacts in dependency in the pom.xml file which is mentioned below. 

**PubSub**

    &lt;dependencyManagement&gt;
      &lt;dependencies&gt;
        &lt;dependency&gt;
          &lt;groupId&gt;com.google.cloud&lt;/groupId&gt;
          &lt;artifactId&gt;libraries-bom&lt;/artifactId&gt;
          &lt;version&gt;26.1.5&lt;/version&gt;
          &lt;type&gt;pom&lt;/type&gt;
          &lt;scope&gt;import&lt;/scope&gt;
        &lt;/dependency&gt;
      &lt;/dependencies&gt;
    &lt;/dependencyManagement&gt;
     
    &lt;dependencies&gt;
      &lt;dependency&gt;
        &lt;groupId&gt;com.google.cloud&lt;/groupId&gt;
        &lt;artifactId&gt;google-cloud-pubsub&lt;/artifactId&gt;
      &lt;/dependency&gt;
     
    &lt;/dependencies&gt;

**PubSub Lite**

    &lt;dependency&gt;
      &lt;groupId&gt;com.google.cloud&lt;/groupId&gt;
      &lt;artifactId&gt;google-cloud-pubsublite&lt;/artifactId&gt;
      &lt;version&gt;1.9.1&lt;/version&gt;
    &lt;/dependency&gt;
    &lt;dependency&gt;
      &lt;groupId&gt;com.google.cloud&lt;/groupId&gt;
      &lt;artifactId&gt;google-cloud-pubsub&lt;/artifactId&gt;
      &lt;version&gt;1.122.1&lt;/version&gt;
    &lt;/dependency&gt;

For more information you can check the Java Client Library for [PubSub](https://github.com/googleapis/java-pubsub) and [PubSub Lite](https://github.com/googleapis/java-pubsublite).

